"- Unspecified: No specific billing terms will be displayed on this "
"document.\n"
"- Fixed Price: A mention is displayed precising the contract type is fixed "
"price.\n"
"- Open Book: A mention is displayed precising the contract type is open "
"book.\n"
"- Per Line: Mixed billing logic where you define individually for each line "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Menentukan tipe kontrak pada dokumen tawaran:\n"
"- Unspecified: Tidak ada termin tagihan spesifik yang akan ditampilkan di "
"dokumen ini.\n"
"- Fixed Price: Ada penjelasan tipe kontrak yaitu fixed price.\n"
"- Open Book: Ada penjelasan tipe kontrak yaitu open book.\n"
"- Per Line: Logika tagihan campur di mana Anda mendefinisikan secara "
"individu untuk setiap item dalam baris."

